data.description: A beautiful brick 2,600 + square ft. family home that sits on 2 lots that total over a half-acre in the Leona Acres Subdivision. This home contains 4BD/3 full bath with split bedroom arrangements, large living room with wood burning fireplace, updated kitchen with plenty of countertop and cabinet space, 2 master suites, game room or second living area, and a security system. Outside features a 2-Car detached garage, additional parking in the driveway, complete privacy fenced yard, inground pool and sprinkler system.
